Alexander Hanson (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexander_Hanson_(actor) 0 Alexander Harald St John Hanson-Akins (born 28 April 1961) is a Norwegian-born British stage actor who has appeared in numerous plays and musicals in the West End, and also on Broadway.
